text: Jan Wyrowiński (20101) Jan Alfons Wyrowiński (born 27 August 1947, Brusy) is a Polish politician and Kashubian activist. He was the chairman of Kashubian- Pomeranian Association in the period 1994–1999.Jan Wyrowinski, Senator RP, official pageSenate of Poland ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:People from Brusy Category:Polish activists
